OL,5,Cleaders
OL,7,FMore than 400 experts have called on
OL,8,Fpolitical leaders to pledge
OL,9,F"ambitious" action on climate change
OL,10,Fif they win the General Election on
OL,11,FJuly 4.
OL,13,FIn an open letter published on Monday,
OL,14,Fthe experts from universities around
OL,15,Fthe country warned that a "failure to
OL,16,Ftackle climate change" is making the
OL,17,FUK a "dangerous" and "insecure" place
OL,18,Fto live.
