OL,3,CMore than 400 climate experts want
OL,4,C'ambitious' action from political
OL,5,Cleaders
OL,7,FThe letter says: "We call on you to
OL,8,Fpledge to an ambitious programme of
OL,9,Fclimate policies that accelerate
OL,10,Faction, in the UK and across the
OL,11,Fworld, both to cut greenhouse gas
OL,12,Femissions and to increase resilience
OL,13,Fto those impacts of climate change
OL,14,Fthat cannot now be avoided.
OL,16,F"Without such a programme, the UK will
OL,17,Fbe shirking its international
OL,18,Fresponsibilities and will be losing
OL,19,Fthe opportunity to promote prosperity
OL,20,Fand peace in the UK and around the
OL,21,Fglobe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
