OL,3,CMore than 400 climate experts want
OL,4,C'ambitious' action from political
OL,5,Cleaders
OL,7,FThe letter continued by outlining five
OL,8,Fpoints of action that the experts hope
OL,9,Fthe Government will adopt once its
OL,10,Fbeen voted into power.
OL,12,FThese include publishing a "strategy
OL,13,Ffor ending the UK's contribution to
OL,14,Fclimate change" and "increasing public
OL,15,Fand private funding for climate change
OL,16,Fmitigation in developing countries."
