OL,4,C'ambitious' action from political
OL,5,Cleaders
OL,7,FIt also called the Government to "lead
OL,8,Fby example internationally on climate
OL,9,Fchange" and "accelerate action across
OL,10,Fall sectors and all parts of the UK to
OL,11,Fadapt and become more resilient to
OL,12,Fthose impacts of climate change."
OL,14,FITV News' Martin Stew breaks down the
OL,15,Fparties' climate pledges
