OL,4,C'ambitious' action from political
OL,5,Cleaders
OL,7,FProfessor Emliy Shuckburgh, who was
OL,8,Fone of the organisers of the letter,
OL,9,Fsaid in a statement: "The UK has just
OL,10,Fexperienced by far the warmest May on
OL,11,Frecord, despite the weather seeming
OL,12,Fmiserable.
OL,14,F"Climate change puts a dark cloud over
OL,15,Fall our futures - as a climate
OL,16,Fscientist I am fearful of what is in
OL,17,Fstore. Many aspects of global
OL,18,Fstability are at risk from ice sheets
OL,19,Fand ocean currents to financial
OL,20,Fsystems, food security and
OL,21,Fgeopolitical order.
