OL,5,Cleaders
OL,7,F"The climate clock is ticking loudly,
OL,8,Four Party Leaders need to listen and
OL,9,Frespond."
OL,11,FThe letter comes as the UK recorded
OL,12,Fits warmest May and spring on record,
OL,13,Fdespite the wet, dull conditions for
OL,14,Fmany parts of the country, according
OL,15,Fto provisional Met Office figures.
OL,17,FMeteorological spring, which covers
OL,18,Fthe months of March, April and May,
OL,19,Fwas also the warmest on record, the
OL,20,Ffigures show.
